"{\"uid\": \"atlantanewsfirst.com-2024-07-28-remembering-centennial-olympic-park-bombing-1996-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ATLANTA, Ga. (Atlanta News First) - As the world gathers in Paris for the 2024 Olympics, Saturday marked a grim anniversary here in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999747035421, \"rank\": 2.4382743249842163e-08, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_First\", \"score\": 0.9999999767086367, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"News First\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_First\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_First\"}, {\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999960846536649, \"rank\": 3.915361684995773e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999747035421, \"rank\": 2.4382743249842163e-08, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the 28th anniversary of the bombing that shook the opening ceremony at the 1996 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eric Rudolph detonated a bomb at Centennial Olympic Park, killing one woman and injuring more than 100 others.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Rudolph\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eric Rudolph\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Rudolph\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Rudolph\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centennial_Olympic_Park_bombing\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.473067732092255e-13, \"text\": \"Centennial Olympic Park\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centennial_Olympic_Park_bombing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centennial_Olympic_Park_bombing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack has left a scar on many people in Atlanta, like Kimberly Krautter, who was working near the blast.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999747035421, \"rank\": 2.4382743249842163e-08, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\", \"score\": 0.9999974698654517, \"rank\": 2.2809551454598987e-06, \"text\": \"Kimberly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody thought--who wasn't immediately where the tower was--thought it was fireworks,\\\" Krautter said.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when you heard the screams, and the scattering and the chaos, my first thought was my crew.\\\"\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Krautter tells us all of her crew made it out okay.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eric Rudolph was captured in North Carolina seven years after the bombing.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end